"{\"uid\": \"intlgymnast.com-news-biles-wins-second-olympic-all-around-title\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Eight years after her first Olympic all-around gold medal in Rio,Simone Bilesof the U.S. was crowned once again the all-around champion at the Bercy arena in Paris on Thursday evening.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 61, \"end\": 64, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9157880102929184e-14, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 158, \"end\": 163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.364081854820162e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her first Olympic all-around gold medal\", \"from\": 18, \"to\": 57}, {\"ngram\": \"Simone Bilesof\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 79}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 80, \"to\": 88}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-around champion\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 135}, {\"ngram\": \"the Bercy arena\", \"from\": 139, \"to\": 154}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday evening\", \"from\": 167, \"to\": 183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With her explosive display of difficulty, Biles, 27, delivered under pressure to record 59.131 for her 9thOlympic medal of her career (sixth gold).\", \"from\": 186, \"to\": 333, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her explosive display\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 212}, {\"ngram\": \"difficulty\", \"from\": 216, \"to\": 226}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 233}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 263}, {\"ngram\": \"her 9thOlympic medal\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 305}, {\"ngram\": \"her career\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 319}, {\"ngram\": \"(sixth gold\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles had an uncharacteristic mistake on bars after her Pak salto, and scored only 13.733, but rebounded with the highest scores of the competition on beam 14.5 and floor 15.066 to take the title.\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 390, \"end\": 399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pak_salto\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pak salto\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pak_salto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pak_salto\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 339}, {\"ngram\": \"an uncharacteristic mistake\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 371}, {\"ngram\": \"bars\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 379}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest scores\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 462}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"beam\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 489}, {\"ngram\": \"floor\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 504}, {\"ngram\": \"the title\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Oh gosh, I mean, I have put in so many numbers on the bars.\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many numbers\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"the bars\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it was an unfortunate mistake, but I knew to just keep pushing and to not give up.\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an unfortunate mistake\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's exactly what you saw out there\\\", Biles said.\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles also received the top score on vault 15.766 for her Yurchenko double pike.\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"the top score\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 768}, {\"ngram\": \"vault\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just ecstatic with my performances tonight.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my performances\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And we still have three finals left for me.\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three finals\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now it's time to have fun and the hard part is over \\\", she said.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"the hard part\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles has qualified to the vault, balance beam and the floor finals.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1044, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"the vault\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1008}, {\"ngram\": \"balance beam\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1022}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor finals\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1043}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She won the vault and floor Olympic gold medals in Rio, and is two time Olympic bronze medalist on balance beam.\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1096, \"end\": 1099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9157880102929184e-14, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the vault and floor Olympic gold medals\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"two time\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic bronze medalist\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"balance beam\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No gymnast had ever repeated as the all-around champion in non-consecutive Olympic games, which makes Biles the first one to do so.\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No gymnast\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"the all-around champion\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1214}, {\"ngram\": \"non-consecutive Olympic games\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1247}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the win Biles also becomes only the third female to have won the Olympic all-around twice, joining Soviet Union'sLarisa LatyninaandV\\u011bra \\u010c\\u00e1zlavsk\\u00e1of Czechoslovakia.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czechoslovakia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.7904677006686821, \"rank\": 0.26325234672297315, \"text\": \"Czechoslovakia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czechoslovakia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czechoslovakia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the win\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"only the third female\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1345}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles also continues a dominant streak for her country, as for the last 20 years now at the Olympics the all-around title has been won by a U.S. gymnast.Carly Pattersonwon in 2004, followed byNastia Liukinin 2008,Gabby Douglasin 2012, Biles in 2016 andSuni Leein 2020.\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1467}, {\"ngram\": \"a dominant streak\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"her country\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngr